overview.en: BeeStore the world's largest block-chain application store. empowers developers and users of standard Apple AppStore and Google Play. and focuses on building applications and services related to block chains
overview.zh: BeeStore全球最大的区块链应用商店 对标苹果AppStore和GooglePlay 赋能开发者和用户 专注于构建与区块链相关的应用程序和服务 未来致力于建立一个全球范围内的以应用分发为 核心的去中心化 高度自治的内容分发生态
